# Atlas Index

The dashboard for every site in this project, provided by `rasa.module.atlas`.
Each site is one file under `sites/<id-block>/site-NNNNNN.md` (sharded on the id,
never by category).

- The rules that govern sites live in **`.claude/atlas-rules.md`**.
- The per-project color key (categories → colors) is **`.claude/atlas-canon.md`**.
- `/atlas index` regenerates the counts + legend + health block below.

**This is a dashboard, not a per-site table.** The generated `atlas.kml` and
`atlas.geojson` are the real at-a-glance rollup — you browse places on a map, not
in a markdown table. (`/atlas export both` regenerates them.)

